title: Allen Choi

Hello! Nice to meet you!
Hi! My name is Allen Choi and I am a 4th year Statistics student here at California Polytechnic State University, San Luis Obispo! I’ll also be continuing my education here for my Master’s in Statistics next year. Some of my hobbies include reading (nonfiction and fiction) as well as running and going to the gym.
